msgstr "Iakhawunti yakho iya kucinywa ngokupheleleyo nge-{purgeDate}. Uphumile. Ukuze urhoxise, ngena kwakhona phambi koko."

#: src/features/user/close-account.tsx:94
msgid "Your account will be scheduled for deletion and you'll be signed out. You can cancel any time before the deletion date by logging back in. Download your data first if you want to keep a copy."
msgstr "Iakhawunti yakho iya kucwangciselwa ukucinywa kwaye uya kuphuma. Ungayirhoxisa nanini na phambi komhla wokucinywa ngokungena kwakhona. Khuphela idatha yakho kuqala ukuba ufuna ukugcina ikopi."

#: src/features/user/replication.tsx:219
msgid "Your account's data on this server will be permanently deleted and you'll be signed out here. Your account stays on your other servers, and you can re-add this one later."
msgstr "Idatha yeakhawunti yakho kule seva iya kucinywa ngokusisigxina kwaye uya kuphuma apha. Iakhawunti yakho ihlala kwezinye iiseva zakho, kwaye ungaphinda uyongeze le seva kamva."

#: src/features/user/data.tsx:180
msgid "Your data"
msgstr "Idatha yakho"

#: src/features/user/data.tsx:113
#~ msgid "Your data is downloading"
#~ msgstr "Idatha yakho iyakhutshelwa"

#: src/features/user/data.tsx:162
msgid "Your private keys are included, encrypted with this passphrase. Store it safely. You'll need it to restore."
msgstr "Izikhiye zakho zobucala ziqukiwe, zikhushulwe ngalo msomiso wesigama. Zigcine ngokukhuselekileyo. Uzidinga ukuze ulungise."
